<li> Happy Mother's Day to the woman who taught me how to love, believe, and forgive.</li>
<li> Your gentle spirit and unwavering faith are a blessing to our family.</li>
<li> Wishing you a day filled with joy and blessings, Mom. You deserve all the happiness in the world.</li>
<li> Thank you for being the best mother, friend, and confidante a person could ask for.</li>
